{"id": "1420969634227687597", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "442792016875749386", "author_name": "tardis10.", "author_bot": false, "content": "始めたばかりなんですが陣営はどこが良いんでしょうか?\n深海が良いと見たんで一応恒常で30連そこ引いてはいたんですがずっとブッパして良いものかよく判らず…アイテムでのキャラ交換はまだしてません。無課金予定、ストーリーは次1-13です。", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:06:01.139000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1420969633963442267", "filename": "IMG_1636.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1001252, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1420969633963442267/IMG_1636.png?ex=6a340959&is=6a32b7d9&hm=a9def9b2e32fd277ab80350ee02f64de6fc60d713de2bc0a55ef26f7cc9b1954&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420970653929967718", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "恒常ガチャはチケット？でのみ引くことをおすすめします\n石を使うのはピックアップのみ", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:10:04.255000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["442792016875749386"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1420969634227687597", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420970725115695246", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "深海だけど、強い理由は前ピックのトゥルーが強かったから", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:10:21.227000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420971128985223249", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーぬきの場合は無料で手に入るものの凸をしにくいオレッタを軸にするか、今ピック中のソレールと合わせるのが良いと思います", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:11:57.517000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420971445512704134", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーはピック終了済だけど、ダフォをリセットして入手は可能です\n(ダフォダリオがバランス調整の影響に引っかかったため、リセット可能な対応されている)", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:13:12.983000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420971805547692093", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "※バランス調整終了した現時点以降に新たに入手したダフォがリセットできるかは未確認", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:14:38.822000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1420979643510689893", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "442792016875749386", "author_name": "tardis10.", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます。恒常は恒常石で引いてて限定に使える石は未使用なんでソレール狙ってみようと思います", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T03:45:47.538000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
